trans-unit.source: Represents the removal of a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> during dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Representa a remoção de um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> durante a atualização dinâmica.
Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: This class can be used by a tracking service to determine which <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s have been removed during a dynamic update.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe pode ser usada por um serviço de controle para determinar qual <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet>s foram removidos durante a atualização dinâmica.

trans-unit.source: An instance of this object is generated for every <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet> that is removed (that is, that existed in the workflow before this dynamic update, but is gone afterward).
trans-unit.target: Uma instância do objeto é gerada para cada <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet> que está sendo removido (ou seja, que existia no fluxo de trabalho antes da atualização dinâmica, mas não existe mais posteriormente).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction" />.
O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removido do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction" /> class by using the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RemovedRuleSetAction" /> usando o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removido do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="removedRuleSetDefinition" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="removedRuleSetDefinition" /> é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets or Sets the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removido do fluxo de trabalho.
O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removido do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> to remove from the workflow is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> a ser removido do fluxo de trabalho é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removido do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removed from the workflow.
trans-unit.target: O nome do <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet" /> removido do fluxo de trabalho.
